 special.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/C6694Va.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>More in the sauce: https://themotherofallnerds.com/keanu-grandma-call/</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/j45lujm</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[moyanerd]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Stay away Anish Kapoor</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/MUWc7Zr</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/oGvrQDP.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/MUWc7Zr</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Albedamned]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Omg it was him</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/GrWFliT</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/TGwf7yj.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>So I work at a tiny Swedish supplier to automotive industries. As I got lunch today at work, by the salad bar in the canteen, I noticed a guy looking very much like Keanu Reeves.

Chuckling about it as I sat down by my colleagues, “It must be fun looking like Keanu Reeves”, I said. 

And yeah, it was him. He’s apparently involved in a motorcycle company, which we supply. I was too star struck to get any real work for the rest of the day. I didn’t want to bother him (celebs should have their privacy), but others that worked with him said he was a super nice guy, really down to earth.

Still a bit shocked he showed up here of all places.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/GrWFliT</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[superapan]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Travel Insurance to Visit Your Own Country</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/K7wYvys</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/tVlZDXw.jpg?1" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/K7wYvys</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[jfoobar]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Great idea.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/8kWl8QQ</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ZQZoXgT.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/FP2RlQ6.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/incsTwN.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>FP Edit: 
