SPECULATION: There are probably orders to join in the invasion, but met by such stiff resistance among Belarusians is making difficult if not impossible.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/dgwsCKF.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>The exercises were originally planned for December. The exercises include over 30,000 troops from 27 member nations, more than double the previously planned amount. This includes faux air battles, troop deployment exercises, etc.
